Reports redundant parentheses.
<!-- tooltip end -->
<p>In expressions:</p>
<pre><code>var x = ((1) + 2) + 3</code></pre>

<p>In arrow function argument lists:</p>
<pre><code>var incrementer = (x) => x + 1</code></pre>

<p>In TypeScript and Flow type declarations:</p>
<pre><code lang="typescript">type Card = (Suit & Rank) | (Suit & Number)</code></pre>
